dsdep (1.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Added S3 model download support
  * Added .env file setup (interactive, copy, template modes)
  * Added AWS credentials management
  * Added --skip-models and --skip-hardening options
  * Improved workflow with 9 steps
  * Better verification of models and environment

 -- Parthiv Ripik <parthiv@ripiktech.com>  Thu, 11 Dec 2024 14:00:00 +0530

dsdep (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * Features:
    - Clone Git repositories
    - Setup conda or venv environments
    - Install dependencies from requirements.txt
    - Deploy systemd service with hardening
    - Automatic log monitoring and restart
    - Deployment verification

